snippet.title: Pop Culture Minefield
snippet.description:
Pop Culture Minefield is your One Stop Shop for all things Pop Culture! 
Movie, Television and Comic news and rumors, as well as exclusive scoops from Mikey Sutton's Geekosity Magazine 
https://streamelements.com/popcultureminefield/tip

A special Thank You to our Patrons
Patron Producers: Jim Woodward  Tina Roberts  John Schmidt  Mr. Tickle Trunk

🔥 Gerry's professional site can be found at 👉 https://gerrykissell.wixsite.com/kissellstudios



On Pop Culture Minefield, Keith and Gerry, you get the latest news on Major Movies and TV shows coming out! DD Crowley does her game reports and reviews.
